content:
Strength:
Press 5-5-5

Metcon:
In teams of 3 perform as many rounds as possible in 20min of:
5 Back Squats (#60/40)
7 Ring Dips
10 Jumping Jacks

*2 team members hold the bar on shoulder height while the 3rd member does a round. If at any time the bar touch the ground - the whole team does 10 Burpees as a penalty*
